{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/ryokan-penginapan-bercitarasa-tradisional-di-jepang-berasa-jepang-tempo-dulu-banget/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Ryokan, Penginapan Bercitarasa Tradisional Di Jepang. Berasa Jepang Tempo Dulu Banget!","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jika bro sis sudah merencanakan untuk berlibur dan mengunjungi negara Jepang, tentu bro sis sudah menyiapkan <em>planning</em> yang berhubungan dengan kunjungan tersebut. Seperti misalnya mengunjungi lokasi-lokasi belanja khas barang otaku yang ada di wilayah Jepang [<a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/lima-besar-lokasi-belanja-otaku-di-jepang/\">5 Besar Lokasi Belanja Otaku di Jepang</a>]. Atau mungkin nongkrong cantik sambil ngopi dan nyobain senjata airsoft gun? <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kultur-themed-cafe-jepang-yang-unik-gun-cafe/\">[Kultur Theme Cafe Jepang yang Unik</a>].  Semuanya bisa dan bakal asyik dilakukan saat berada di Jepang.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Faktor penting yang tidak bisa diabaikan adalah tempat menginap selama berada di Jepang. Bro sis bisa memanfaatkan fasilitas normal seperti hotel. Jepang dipastika tidak akan kekurangan hotel karena negara ini merupakan tujuan wisata terkenal sedunia. Budget terbatas? Bro sis bisa memanfaatkan penginapan-penginapan murah meriah seperti internet café yang juga menyediakan fasilitas menginap [<a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/warnet-di-akihabara-jepang-yang-lebih-mirip-hotel-daripada-internet-cafe/\">Warnet di Akihabara Jepang yang Lebih Mirip Hotel Daripada Internet Cafe</a>]</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nah… Ada pula pilihan lain, bro sis. Dan menurut saya ini akan lebih seru, karena kita bakal merasakan nuansa Jepang tempo dulu yang kental ketimbang hotel standard maupun warnet. Pilihan tempat menginap tersebut adalah “Ryokan”.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_37088\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-37088\" data-attachment-id=\"37088\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ryokan-penginapan-bercitarasa-tradisional-di-jepang-berasa-jepang-tempo-dulu-banget/attachment/isi-18-17/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-18.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Definisi Ryokan dalam bahasa Inggris. Sumber gambar: japantravel-centre.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Definisi Ryokan dalam bahasa Inggris. Sumber gambar: japantravel-centre.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-18.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-18.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-37088\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-18.jpg\" alt=\"Definisi Ryokan dalam bahasa Inggris. Sumber gambar: japantravel-centre.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-37088\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Definisi Ryokan dalam bahasa Inggris. Sumber gambar: japantravel-centre.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ryokan adalah penginapan tradisional. Jenis penginapan ini sudah berusia sangat panjang. Jauh lebih panjang daripada jaringan hotel Barat yang masuk ke Jepang pasca Perang Dunia Kedua. Ryokan mulai populer di era Edo, yaitu tahun 1603 hingga 1868. Jauh lebih tua dari umur Republik Indonesia ya, bro sis? Hehehe. Saat situasi politik Jepang mulai stabil sejak era Tokugawa Shogunate, pembangunan infrastruktur mulai dilakukan pemerintah. Untuk menjalankan hal tersebut, pemerintah membuat sistem yang disebut “sankinkotai”, dimana pemimpin-pemimpin daerah (atau Tuan Tanah yang disebut Daimyo) diwajibkan mengirim warga mereka dalam jumlah tertentu secara reguler ke ibukota Edo (kini Tokyo) dimana pemerintah pusat berada. Di sepanjang jalan menuju Edo, para Daimyo membangun <em>‘rest area’</em> untuk mereka (disebut honjin) dimana di sekeliling area tersebut juga dibangun kompleks penginapan (disebut shukubamachi) dan toko untuk traveler yang akan menuju Edo (disebut hatago). Honjin dan hatago dapat dikatakan sebagai cikal bakal dari konsep Ryokan sekarang.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_37073\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-37073\" data-attachment-id=\"37073\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ryokan-penginapan-bercitarasa-tradisional-di-jepang-berasa-jepang-tempo-dulu-banget/attachment/isi-13-25/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-13.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Ryokan. Sumber gambar: japan-guide.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Ryokan. Sumber gambar: japan-guide.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-13.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-13.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-37073\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-13.jpg\" alt=\"Ryokan. Sumber gambar: japan-guide.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-37073\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ryokan. Sumber gambar: japan-guide.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jika mencari padanan Ryokan dengan tempat yang sama di Indonesia, mungkin losmen tradisional bisa jadi pembanding. Generasi zaman sekarang mungkin enggak familiar dengan serial drama televisi “Losmen” di TVRI dulu, tapi menurut saya Ryokan dan Losmen punya karakteristik yang sama. Bernuansa tradisional.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_37085\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-37085\" data-attachment-id=\"37085\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ryokan-penginapan-bercitarasa-tradisional-di-jepang-berasa-jepang-tempo-dulu-banget/attachment/isi-17-17/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-17.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Serial Losmen di TVRI jadul. Sumber gambar: youtube.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Serial Losmen di TVRI jadul. Sumber gambar: youtube.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-17.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-17.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-37085\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-17.jpg\" alt=\"Serial Losmen di TVRI jadul. Sumber gambar: youtube.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-37085\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Serial Losmen di TVRI jadul. Sumber gambar: youtube.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Salah satu ciri khas di Ryokan ini, selain <em>feel</em> tradisionalnya, adalah para tamu tidak diperbolehkan memakai sepatu/alas kaki selain yang disediakan pihak Ryokan. Semua alas kaki harus dilepas di pintu masuk. Pegawai Ryokan akan menyimpannya di loker dan memberikan bro sis sandal Ryokan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_37064\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-37064\" data-attachment-id=\"37064\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ryokan-penginapan-bercitarasa-tradisional-di-jepang-berasa-jepang-tempo-dulu-banget/attachment/isi-10-47/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-10-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Locker sepatu Ryokan. Sumber gambar: web-japan.org\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Locker sepatu Ryokan. Sumber gambar: web-japan.org&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-10-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-10-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-37064\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-10-1.jpg\" alt=\"Locker sepatu Ryokan. Sumber gambar: web-japan.org\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-37064\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Locker sepatu Ryokan. Sumber gambar: web-japan.org</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_37079\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-37079\" data-attachment-id=\"37079\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ryokan-penginapan-bercitarasa-tradisional-di-jepang-berasa-jepang-tempo-dulu-banget/attachment/isi-15-18/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-15.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Setelah melapor ke resepsionis, tamu akan diantar ke kamar. Sumber gambar: web-japan.org\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Setelah melapor ke resepsionis, tamu akan diantar ke kamar. Sumber gambar: web-japan.org&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-15.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-15.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-37079\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-15.jpg\" alt=\"Setelah melapor ke resepsionis, tamu akan diantar ke kamar. Sumber gambar: web-japan.org\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-37079\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Setelah melapor ke resepsionis, tamu akan diantar ke kamar. Sumber gambar: web-japan.org</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nuansa kamar penginapan di Ryokan adalah tradisional seperti yang sudah jadi ciri khas Ryokan sejak dahulu kala. Jadi persiapkan diri melihat tatami/alas lantai kamar khas rumah-rumah Jepang tradisional, hiasan bambu, pintu geser yang terbuat dari kertas (iya, seperti pintu yang sering kita lihat di anime), dan futon. Tidak ada ranjang modern seperti hotel kebanyakan. Tamu akan tidur di atas futon, ranjang tradisional kultur Jepang.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_37082\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-37082\" data-attachment-id=\"37082\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ryokan-penginapan-bercitarasa-tradisional-di-jepang-berasa-jepang-tempo-dulu-banget/attachment/isi-16-17/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-16.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Pintu geser yang terbuat dari kertas. Sumber gambar: kashiwaya.org\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Pintu geser yang terbuat dari kertas. Sumber gambar: kashiwaya.org&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-16.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-16.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-37082\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-16.jpg\" alt=\"Pintu geser yang terbuat dari kertas. Sumber gambar: kashiwaya.org\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-37082\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Pintu geser yang terbuat dari kertas. Sumber gambar: kashiwaya.org</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_37061\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-37061\" data-attachment-id=\"37061\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ryokan-penginapan-bercitarasa-tradisional-di-jepang-berasa-jepang-tempo-dulu-banget/attachment/isi-9-58/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-9-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Futon. Sleeping mattress tradisional Jepang. Sumber gambar: tripadvisor.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Futon. Sleeping mattress tradisional Jepang. Sumber gambar: tripadvisor.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-9-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-9-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-37061\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-9-1.jpg\" alt=\"Futon. Sleeping mattress tradisional Jepang. Sumber gambar: tripadvisor.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-37061\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Futon. Sleeping mattress tradisional Jepang. Sumber gambar: tripadvisor.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ciri khas lainnya dari Ryokan adalah pemandian bersama yang disebut Oburo. Beberapa Ryokan menyediakan tempat mandi dan toilet di dalam kamar tamu, tapi lebih banyak yang menyediakan <em>shared bath tub</em> seperti Oburo ini. Selain indoor, ada pula Oburo outdoor (disebut Rotenburo) yang tertutup dari pandangan luar (untuk menjaga privasi) namun penggunanya dapat menikmati suasana outdoor sembari meminum sake dan memandang langit yang luas.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_37067\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-37067\" data-attachment-id=\"37067\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ryokan-penginapan-bercitarasa-tradisional-di-jepang-berasa-jepang-tempo-dulu-banget/attachment/isi-11-36/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Yok! Mandi bareng! *ditabok. Sumber gambar: youinjapan.net\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Yok! Mandi bareng! *ditabok. Sumber gambar: youinjapan.net&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-11.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-11.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-37067\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-11.jpg\" alt=\"Yok! Mandi bareng! *ditabok. Sumber gambar: youinjapan.net\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-37067\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Oburo, orang Indonesia pasti gak biasa mandi disini. Sumber gambar: youinjapan.net</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_37070\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-37070\" data-attachment-id=\"37070\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ryokan-penginapan-bercitarasa-tradisional-di-jepang-berasa-jepang-tempo-dulu-banget/attachment/isi-12-28/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-12.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Privasi terjamin. Sumber gambar: wikimedia.org\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Privasi terjamin. Sumber gambar: wikimedia.org&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-12.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-12.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-37070\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-12.jpg\" alt=\"Privasi terjamin. Sumber gambar: wikimedia.org\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-37070\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Privasi terjamin. Sumber gambar: wikimedia.org</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Beberapa Ryokan menerapkan jam malam untuk menjaga kenyamanan tamu, jadi jika bro sis menginap di Ryokan perlu tahu aturan yang berlaku disana.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ryokan tersebar di berbagai lokasi Jepang, termasuk di Kyoto dan Tokyo. Penginapan bercita rasa tradisional ini tidak saja menarik minat turis mancanegara namun warga Jepang sekalipun banyak yang menyenangi fasilitas di Ryokan. Jadi bisnis ini masih akan tetap hidup untuk waktu yang lama.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_37076\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-37076\" data-attachment-id=\"37076\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ryokan-penginapan-bercitarasa-tradisional-di-jepang-berasa-jepang-tempo-dulu-banget/attachment/isi-14-21/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-14.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Ryokan di Kyoto. Sumber gambar: insidekyoto.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Ryokan di Kyoto. Sumber gambar: insidekyoto.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-14.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-14.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-37076\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/isi-14.jpg\" alt=\"Ryokan di Kyoto. Sumber gambar: insidekyoto.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-37076\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ryokan di Kyoto. Sumber gambar: insidekyoto.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>So,</em> apa bro sis berminat mencoba penginapan bercita-rasa tradisional seperti Ryokan ini? Bagi pengalamannya ya, bro sis! hehehe.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"3590d227-ad54-5c91-a5e8-b010faf207bb"}}}